WEBVTT

00:11:28.226 --> 00:11:32.130
for whom country living
is preferable to the urban life.

00:11:33.337 --> 00:11:36.719
When we choose between options
that are on a par,

00:11:36.743 --> 00:11:39.854
we can do something
really rather remarkable.

00:11:40.495 --> 00:11:43.350
We can put our very selves
behind an option.

00:11:44.325 --> 00:11:46.109
Here's where I stand.

00:11:46.910 --> 00:11:50.108
Here's who I am, I am for banking.

00:11:50.132 --> 00:11:52.267
I am for chocolate donuts.

00:11:52.291 --> 00:11:53.859
(Laughter)

00:11:54.370 --> 00:11:58.697
This response in hard choices
is a rational response,

00:11:58.721 --> 00:12:01.397
but it's not dictated
by reasons given to us.